lead_paragraph: Wales talisman Gareth Bale set up the first goal and scored twice, including a late penalty, as the Euro 2016 semi-finalists won 4-0 in their opening Group D World Cup qualifier on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Bale Spurs Wales to Comfortable 4-0 Win Over Moldova
